# SteamID-64-generator
generate all valable steamID 64 for an steam account from an steamID 64 or 32


# Exemple (see Exemple.txt)
```
#	| SteamID 64 : 76561197960287930
#	| SteamID 32 : 22202
0	| 76561193665320634
1	| 76561197960287930
2	| 76561202255255226
3	| 76561206550222522
4	| 76561210845189818
5	| 76561215140157114
6	| 76561219435124410
7	| 76561223730091706
8	| 76561228025059002
9	| 76561232320026298
```
